genresAdvancedInfo.name: beach music
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Beach music is a genre that originated in the coastal areas of the southeastern United States. It is known for its upbeat tempo, catchy melodies, and lyrics that often celebrate the joys of summer and the beach lifestyle. The music is often performed by large bands with horns and vocal harmonies, and it has been popular since the 1940s.
